            "title": "《本周港股前瞻》－－美伊談判無果 恒指今勢低開",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2026年4月13日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n<span class=\"column\"><a href=\"https://search.hkej.com/template/fulltextsearch/php/search.php?q=本周港股前瞻\">本周港股前瞻</a></span>\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">美伊談判無果 恒指今勢低開<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/04/13/4369743_360baed7a25f1849520089db90047ac8.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/04/13/4369743_360baed7a25f1849520089db90047ac8_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/04/13/4369743_360baed7a25f1849520089db90047ac8.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/04/13/4369743_360baed7a25f1849520089db90047ac8.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n美伊周日舉行第三輪談判無果，據報雙方在霍爾木茲海峽問題上仍有嚴重分歧，俗稱「周末黑期」的新加坡周末香港HS50現貨昨跌到25600點至25700點區間，較恒指上周五收市25893點低水200多點。分析指出，除非美伊談判再度重啟，否則市場情緒將重返避險狀態。\n憧憬美伊本輪談判有進展，環球股市造好，恒指...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
